<plot>Cree playwright Floyd Favel travels from Saskatchewan to explore the Tunguska region of Russia in order to learn more about the Tunguska Event, a massive explosion that occurred there in 1908, for reasons unknown. In his journey he explores the common bonds between the Cree and the Evenki people of Tunguska, making it a journey of both historical and spiritual discovery.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?597419</url></doc>
